Scope of this license: This MIT License covers the source code, notebooks,
and scripts in this repository (src/, notebooks/). It does NOT cover:

1. The underlying datasets (data/), which originate from the Government of
   India (Ministry of Road Transport and Highways / Vahan via NITI Aayog
   ICED, Ministry of Power, Ministry of Heavy Industries, MoSPI, Census of
   India, National Commission on Population). These are public data
   released under the respective source agencies' own open-data terms.
   See docs/source_registry.md for the direct URL and publisher of each
   dataset.

2. The synopsis / capstone report (reports/), which is academic coursework
   submitted for QM640: Data Analytics Capstone at Walsh College. It is
   shared here for reviewer transparency and reproducibility, not for
   reuse or redistribution as coursework by others.
